      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa riepilogo sollecito                                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-rie-slc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da stampare                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-slc-snx-ads        not  = "S" and
                     w-slc-snx-api        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-rie-slc-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Interlinee di separazione da corpo              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione numero righe necessarie      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      2                    to   w-stp-rie-slc-nrn      .
           add       w-slc-ids-rie        to   w-stp-rie-slc-nrn      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se righe residue sufficienti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        p-res                >    w-stp-rie-slc-nrn
                     go to stp-rie-slc-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Reintestazione                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   rei-mod-tes-000      thru rei-mod-tes-999        .
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to stp-rie-slc-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salto interlinee di separazione             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-rie-slc-120.
       stp-rie-slc-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Esecuzione interlinee vuote di separazione  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "L+"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      w-slc-ids-rie        to   p-lin                  .
           add       1                    to   p-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
