                     go to stp-rie-slc-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione numero righe di testo        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      5                    to   w-stp-rie-slc-nrt      .
       stp-rie-slc-140.
           if        w-stp-rie-slc-nrt    =    zero
                     go to stp-rie-slc-200.
           if        w-slc-rdt-rie
                    (w-stp-rie-slc-nrt)   =    spaces
                     subtract 1           from w-stp-rie-slc-nrt
                     go to stp-rie-slc-140.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scansione righe di testo           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
